Get Predictions in Flow Builder

Use the Einstein Discovery core action in Flow Builder to get predictions, top predictors, and improvements.
A flow collects data and performs actions in your Salesforce org or an external system. In Flow Builder, add an Action element to the flow, select the Einstein Discovery category, then select a deployed model from the Action field.

To view predictions, improvements, and related details, users must have the View Einstein Discovery Recommendations permission assigned to their Salesforce account.
To configure the Einstein Discovery core action, see [Flow Builder](#).

Assign Einstein Discovery Permission Sets to Users.
